casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Alfred PETROSSIAN, Defendant-Petitioner. C-343 September Term 2017
079552 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 17, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001257-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
